At seven lakes there are many classes relating to photography, graphic design, and animation. one such class is digital arts and animation where students learn about basic animation, and they learn how to use much different adobe software. the next class is advanced digital arts and animation where students learn even more advanced graphic design, and they have the opportunity to gain an adobe suite certification. one of the newer classes at seven lakes is animation 1, which teaches students how to use many different animation software not just including adobe. and commercial photography 1 and 2 teach students advanced media techniques
